title: Data_CCU_89_reordered.csv
description: Developed by Green & Mehr (1997), the dataset was used in a Fast-and-Frugal tree, which an emergency-room doctor could use to decide whether a patient concerned about a possible heart attack should be sent to the coronary care unit (CCU) or a regular nursing-bed.

title: Data_CMC_400_reordered.csv
description: Obtained from the UCI Machine Learning Repository and is a subset of the 1987 National Indonesia Contraceptive Survey. Cases are samples of married women who were either not pregnant or did not know if they were pregnant at the time of the interview.
